'''Paddy Wallace''' is a British actor. He is best known for his roles in television, such as ''Doctors'' and ''London Irish'' and in films such as ''Survivors''.

In [[Season 5]] he will portray a "Lead Kingsguard"<ref>[http://www.spotlight.com/2259-1278-6786]</ref>, presumably [[Kingsguard#Current roster|one of the Kingsguard members]] already established by name but who have only been played by extras in the past: Ser [[Boros Blount]], Ser [[Preston Greenfield]], Ser [[Arys Oakheart]], or Ser [[Balon Swann]].
